item.description: About Anjin Anjin Liu is a Postdoctoral Research Associate in the A/DRsch Centre for Artificial Intelligence, Faculty of Engineering and Information Technology, University of Technology Sydney. He received the BIT degree (Honour) at the University of Sydney in 2012. His research interests include concept drift detection, adaptive data stream learning, multi-stream learning, machine learning and big data analytics
